                <blockquote class="mbr-fonts-style display-4">
                <h5 class="mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-2"><strong> IMPORTANT</strong></h5>
                A bitcoin wallet should not be used for long-term storage. Instead, bitcoin or its key should be stored in a secure wallet such as one that uses a multi-signature facility for security.</blockquote>
