                    2. Personal Documents
                </h4>
                <p class="mbr-text mbr-fonts-style display-7">
                    The U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission requires users to verify their identities when registering for digital wallets as part of its Anti-Money Laundering Policy. In order to buy and sell bitcoin, you will need to verify your identity using several personal documents including your driver’s license and Social Security number (SSN).</p>
