                <h4 class="mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4 display-5">
                    3. Secure Internet Connection
                </h4>
                <p class="mbr-text mbr-fonts-style display-7">
                    If you choose to trade bitcoin online, use discretion about when and where you access your digital wallet. Trading bitcoin on an insecure or public wifi network is not recommended and may make you more susceptible to attacks from hackers.</p>
